      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for your next adventure? This well-maintained vehicle is in good condition and offers a fantastic driving experience! It has been cared for over the years, showing some minor signs of use that come with regular enjoyment, but it remains reliable, clean, and ready to hit the road. It\u2019s a solid, dependable choice for anyone looking for quality and value in their next ride!",
